Class ItemizedOverlay<Item extends OverlayItem>

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultItemizedOverlay
public abstract class ItemizedOverlay<Item extends OverlayItem>
extends Overlay
implements Overlay.Snappable

ItemizedOverlay is a base overlay used to group OverlayItems. This overlay class handles drawing of items from north to south on the map and also handles focus changes.
